		<!-- ===== LEADER ABILITY: 精铺 ===== -->
		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_HAPPY_NAME">
			<Text>Precise Layout</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_HAPPY_NAME">
			<Text>精铺</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_HAPPY_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Non-capital cities within 6 tiles of your [ICON_Capital] Capital receive +10% to all yields, with an additional +10% for every 10 [ICON_Citizen] Population (Max 50%). Non-capital cities more than 6 tiles from your Capital receive -100% to all yields. [ICON_Movement] Settlers receive +1 Movement per turn.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_HAPPY_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>首都 [ICON_Capital] 6单元格范围内的非首都城市 +10% 全产出，每有10 [ICON_Citizen] 人口再 +10% 全产出（最高 +50%）。所有6单元格外的非首都城市 -100% 全产出。开拓者每回合 +1 [ICON_Movement] 移动力。</Text>
		</Row>

		<!-- ===== CIV ABILITY: 快乐的人民 ===== -->
		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_HAPPY_NAME">
			<Text>Happy People</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_HAPPY_NAME">
			<Text>快乐的人民</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_HAPPY_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Start with the [ICON_TechBoosted] Astrology Eureka. [ICON_District] Holy Site buildings provide +1 [ICON_Housing] Housing each. All cities receive +10 [ICON_Amenities] Amenities. +0.1 [ICON_Food] Food, [ICON_Production] Production, [ICON_Gold] Gold, [ICON_Science] Science, [ICON_Faith] Faith, and [ICON_Culture] Culture per [ICON_Citizen] Population. Cities with 10 or more [ICON_Citizen] Population double this bonus.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_HAPPY_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>开局拥有占星术尤里卡，圣地建筑 +1 [ICON_Housing] 住房。城市宜居度 +10 [ICON_Amenities]，每个 [ICON_Citizen] 人口 +0.1 全产出，10个 [ICON_Citizen] 人口以上的城市翻倍。</Text>
		</Row>

